  <summary date="2022-05-13T17:17:57Z" status="Introduced in House">Zero-Emission Homes Act of 2021

This bill directs the Department of Energy to establish a Zero-Emission Homes Program that provides rebates to homeowners and owners of multifamily buildings for qualified electrification projects (e.g., electric stoves or heat pumps).</summary>
